decks.notes: This deck focuses on fast mana generation and devotion to green to enable powerful ramp and aggression. It utilizes cards like Llanowar Elves and Elvish Mystic to accelerate mana, while Nykthos, Shrine to Nyx enhances devotion to green. Oath of Nissa helps with card selection, while Skysovereign, Consul Flagship provides an aggressive threat. Kiora, Behemoth Beckoner and Cavalier of Thorns offer additional ramp and card advantage. Karn, the Great Creator has utility to find artifacts, and Lovestruck Beast provides extra aggression. Storm the Festival is a powerful card to generate multiple creatures. Lair of the Hydra and Boseiju, Who Endures provide additional utility.
